  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Researchers are trying to understand the effect of educating patients and encouraging shared
      decision making on rates of CT scanning in head injured patients by using an already
      developed app and observing the effect on the health care provider.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
